  <brief_title>Pneumoperitoneum and Gynecological Laparoscopic Surgery: An Observational Clinical Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact Of Posture and Prolonged Pneumoperitoneum on Intra-Operative and Postoperative Outcomes During Gynecological Laparoscopic Surgery: An Observational Clinical Study</official_title>
